Sometimes, we have to apply specific conditions, given the hand or a single suit and take a restricted decision.
For example thoughts as: 
"There is nothing to be done if diamonds are 3-1. But if they are 2-2, than I have to...."
 or
"If spades are 4-1, I'm always down. To make my contract I need them.... and then hearts would be .... 
so I have to place Queen....."|
